    "name": "La Salamanca",
    "steam_appid": 3025180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/c25824a947ffa3612a19d6c85427c6e0.poster.avif?t=1760729328\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/c25824a947ffa3612a19d6c85427c6e0.webm?t=1760729328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/c25824a947ffa3612a19d6c85427c6e0.mp4?t=1760729328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>《萨拉曼卡》</strong>中，你将扮演一名来自阿根廷的年轻男子。他的所有朋友在去圣地亚哥-德尔埃斯特罗旅行时神秘失踪后，他必须在他们约定的地方寻找他们：一个叫做“埃尔波塔尔”的古老而黑暗的公寓楼，一个看似“舒适”的地方，但实际上并非如此...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>受阿根廷当地传说的启发</strong>，你将不得不深入这个地狱般的场所，躲避它的恶灵，最终揭露你的同事们发生了什么以及这个地方真正的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/9ffbbd816a8ac7c1f88fee27af7596c9.poster.avif?t=1760729328\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/9ffbbd816a8ac7c1f88fee27af7596c9.webm?t=1760729328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/9ffbbd816a8ac7c1f88fee27af7596c9.mp4?t=1760729328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  这是一款心理恐怖游戏，它将你沉浸在一个由阿根廷北部传说启发的故事中。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  令人兴奋的气氛将让即使是最勇敢的人在整个游戏中保持警惕。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  游戏采用章节结构，每个章节和关卡都有不同的玩法，以彼此区分。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  为了在故事中前进并躲避怪物，你需要解开多个谜题来锻炼大脑。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  可怕的怪物和恶魔，你需要根据它们的行为和周围的环境，制定不同的策略来对付它们。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/0b9c1c13d44dd8c1480c5242ea538d40.poster.avif?t=1760729328\" width=616 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/0b9c1c13d44dd8c1480c5242ea538d40.webm?t=1760729328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3025180/extras/0b9c1c13d44dd8c1480c5242ea538d40.mp4?t=1760729328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阿根廷制造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是 <strong>Carpincho Studio</strong>，一群来自阿根廷（大部分来自罗萨里奥）的年轻业余开发者。我们热爱游戏，玩游戏和开发游戏都是我们的激情所在，这也是我们作为一个团队决定最终发布我们的第一款游戏 <strong>“La Salamanca”</strong> 的原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们也喜欢水豚。有史以来最好的动物。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 简体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
